  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"245\" data-backw=\"578\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicKzZyFicCTnjVYuHG9dpCo2WjVrZKZKOB3rWwudmD1dauWWed387hubJw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-imgfileid=\"505181315\" data-ratio=\"0.42421875\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=412d5f86&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicKzZyFicCTnjVYuHG9dpCo2WjVrZKZKOB3rWwudmD1dauWWed387hubJw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：定慧</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">你花大价钱买的顶级GPU，可能30%时间都在「发呆」——不是算力不够，而是数据喂不上。这个被严重低估的AI困境，正在吞噬无数企业的真金白银。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:24px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">今天AI算力中心正在上演一场「魔幻现实」：</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">几十万一张的顶级GPU，三成时间都在「饿着肚子」干等数据。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">AI浪潮中一个被严重低估的困境正浮出水面：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">数据流不动</span>，导致昂贵的GPU算力在「空转」中白白消耗。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">在这一行业背景下，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">XSKY星辰天合</span>近日举办了AIMesh产品战略发布会，旨在破解这一核心效率瓶颈。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">业界普遍观察到，AI训练中因I/O等待导致的GPU利用率低下已成常态，一些场景下顶级算力有近30%的时间在等待数据，无法满负荷运转。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">这一效率问题的背后，是AI基础设施面临的深刻挑战。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">随着大模型算法日益同质化，企业真正的差异化优势越来越依赖于自身独有的「专有数据」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 48px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">这些承载核心经验与智慧的数字资产，因安全与合规要求必须留存于私有环境，其高效转化能力直接决定了AI转型的成败。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 8px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px 8px 24px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75;&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;body&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">01隐形的高墙</span></strong></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">AI进化的道路上，横亘着三堵无形的高墙。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">第一堵是</span><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">IO</span></strong><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">墙</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。计算芯片的吞吐速度狂奔，存储系统的读写速度却被远远甩在身后，导致昂贵的GPU计算单元时常陷入「无米下锅」的空转状态。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">第二堵是</span><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">内存墙</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。模型参数量爆发式增长，狠狠撞上了GPU显存容量的物理天花板，限制了模型的规模和想象力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">第三堵则是</span><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">重力墙</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。数据一旦形成规模，就像拥有了质量，跨地域、跨集群流动的成本和延迟急剧上升，形成了新的、更难以打破的数据孤岛。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 48px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">这三道关卡共同构成了AI工厂的「栓塞」，让数据——这个智能时代的关键燃料——无法高效转化为实际价值与竞争优势。这正是「算力在等待数据的声音，也是资金在燃烧的声音」这一行业共识的根源。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 8px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px 8px 24px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75;&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;body&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">02十年磨一剑</span></strong></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">面对这三堵墙，行业惯性的思路是「堆硬件」——用更快的SSD、更贵的HBM内存来强行闯关。但这无疑是一条成本指数级飙升的不归路。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">XSKY认为破局的关键在于</span><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">架构创新</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">这一思路建立在长期的实践积累之上。成立十年来，XSKY星辰天合已肩负着中国核心产业超过5500PB关键数据的安全重任。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 48px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">过去三年，在复杂多变的市场环境中，该公司实现了超过50%的逆势高增长，全闪存产品占比翻了三倍达到35%，并成功跨越了单集群百PB级部署的技术门槛。在金融、运营商、自动驾驶等对性能与可靠性有严苛要求的领域，其全闪存储架构已经过规模化实战检验，为新一代架构革新奠定了基础。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 8px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px 8px 24px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75;&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;body&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">03三网合一的「速通术」</span></strong></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">本次发布的核心——AIMesh，正是这场架构创新的集大成者。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">它被定义为面向「AI工厂」的</span><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">数据与内存网</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，核心思路是用一套「三网合一」的柔性网络，替代传统僵化的存储架构。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"317\" data-backw=\"562\" data-ratio=\"0.563855421686747\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-w=\"830\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7dd3a94e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3LvS1O5vdtaic6Xav8NPJdMOXDurYZ6rEGibIjunVQNQF4hlbLeF1OjGmg8eXEoydAPQTZf27MN2rg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">第一张网是</span></strong><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">训练数据</span></strong><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">网MeshFS</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，专攻IO墙。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">它并非从零开始，而是将XSKY深耕七年的企业级文件系统XGFS，与代表极致性能的XSEA全闪底座深度融合。MeshFS在保持对POSIX、S3、HDFS等全协议兼容的同时，实现了性能的线性飞跃。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">实测数据显示，其</span><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">顺序读带宽比主流方案提升30%，顺序写带宽更是超出50%</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，能让数据如电流般极速供给GPU，彻底解决训练中的I/O等待问题。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"317\" data-backw=\"562\" data-ratio=\"0.563855421686747\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-w=\"830\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c1170ebe&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3LvS1O5vdtaic6Xav8NPJdMPx3wOZPVkBFUY0dvr49YjQian8GO2c6zOZf5bmNlUvzUk4EUzEJUiasg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">第二张网是全局对象网MeshSpace</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，旨在推倒重力墙。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">其目标是构建EB级别的全局非结构化数据平台。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">通过创新的Global Namespace全局命名空间，它能将分散在不同地域、不同云上的物理存储集群，抽象为一个统一的「逻辑存储池」。对业务而言，访问数据无需再感知其物理位置，真正实现「一个入口，联通全域」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">其底层引擎已进入「单桶百万OPS时代」，大块数据写入性能提升近50%，延迟降低30%，让海量数据的自由流动成为可能。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"317\" data-backw=\"562\" data-ratio=\"0.563855421686747\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-w=\"830\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a84ad5ee&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3LvS1O5vdtaic6Xav8NPJdMC88CKavgGYSg134ZczjGmHicZAy2Af42KqsW0rUWfPEjhiaXcrMWBpnQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">第三张网是推理内存网MeshFusion</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，直接冲击最棘手的内存墙。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">它通过软件栈将本地SSD资源突破物理内存限制，转为面向KVCache的「持久化内存」方案。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 48px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">该方案能以</span><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">约1%的附加硬件成本</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，实现接近纯内存方案的性能，在资源极端受限的特定场景下，甚至能凭借更优的I/O调度实现20%的性能反超，为承载百万字超长上下文的AI推理应用，提供了极具成本效益的解决方案。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 8px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px 8px 24px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75;&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;body&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">04中立的「营盘」</span></strong></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">在技术路线快速更迭的「百模大战」中，企业面临的核心焦虑之一在于技术绑定风险。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">选择与某一特定算力或架构深度绑定，可能意味着未来的灵活性丧失。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"317\" data-backw=\"562\" data-ratio=\"0.563855421686747\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-w=\"830\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c0ba2537&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3LvS1O5vdtaic6Xav8NPJdMTJbNMXVtfGggLUJ6fZWlovbXh90VPqkX6N5Zgm3uvnMjia6wG0gVfng%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">对此，XSKY星辰天合明确的战略选择是：</span><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">开放解耦，做中立的数据底座</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">这一选择的底层逻辑源于对技术生命周期的洞察：尖端算力硬件的黄金生命周期可能仅为3-5年，而企业的核心数据资产则需要存续10年甚至20年以上。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">因此，需要用确定性的、稳固的数据底座能力，去支撑上层快速迭代、充满不确定性的算力竞争。这便是「数据常青」理念的内涵。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">AIMesh的设计完全贯穿了这一原则。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">它不绑定任何特定品牌的算力芯片或云环境，致力于为企业提供一致、标准的数据服务接口。这种中立性与开放性，使其能够融入多元化的技术生态。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">长期合作的国际芯片巨头英特尔认为，该方案「精准击中了当前AI基础设施的痛点」，其软硬协同的设计思路能充分发挥硬件潜能。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">从云计算时代就开始并肩合作的平台伙伴ZStack则视其为「期待已久的‘最佳组合’升级」，其AI算力平台与AIMesh在缓解I/O瓶颈、优化推理成本方面高度契合。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 48px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">而头部AI科技公司MiniMax的反馈也证实，其混合云架构下的「数据孤岛」难题，正需要MeshSpace这类全局数据管理方案来解决，因为「业务无需感知数据物理位置」的特性将极大简化数据使用。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 8px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px 8px 24px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75;&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;body&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">结语</span></strong></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">从2015年以软件定义存储打破硬件黑盒，到2017年用统一平台打通数据协议壁垒，再到2022年提前布局全闪</span></strong><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">AI</span></strong><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">底座</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，XSKY的十年步伐始终踩在技术范式转换的节点上。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">如今，随着AIMesh的发布，这家公司将自己的角色明确为</span><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">「数据资产的守门人」和「</span></strong><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">AI</span></strong><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">之路的加速器」</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">三网合一的AIMesh，其价值不止于性能参数的提升，更在于它试图以中立、开放的架构，为企业构建一个能够穿越技术周期的、稳固的「数据营盘」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">在这个算力与算法如流水般迭代的时代，让企业独有的数据资产得以常青，成为支撑其智能化转型最持久、最可靠的基石。</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "XSKY 发布 AIMesh，通过“三网合一”架构创新，旨在解决 AI 计算中 GPU 空转、模型显存限制、数据孤岛等问题，为企业提供中立、开放、高效的 AI 数据底座。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "XSKY 发布 AIMesh，通过“三网合一”架构创新，旨在解决 AI 计算中 GPU 空转、模型显存限制、数据孤岛等问题，为企业提供中立、开放、高效的 AI 数据底座。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了 XSKY 星辰天合推出的 AIMesh 产品战略，旨在解决当前 AI 算力中心面临的 GPU 利用率低下、数据 I/O 瓶颈、模型内存限制及数据孤岛等核心挑战。文章指出，AI 训练中 GPU 高达 30%时间因数据喂不上而空转，是行业普遍存在的痛点。AIMesh 通过“三网合一”的架构创新，包括解决 IO 墙的训练数据网 MeshFS、解决重力墙的全局对象网 MeshSpace 和解决内存墙的推理内存网 MeshFusion，显著提升了数据吞吐、实现全局数据统一管理，并以低成本提供持久化内存方案。XSKY 强调 AIMesh 作为中立数据底座，不绑定特定算力或云环境，致力于保障企业数据资产“常青”，赢得包括 MiniMax、英特尔、ZStack 在内伙伴的认可。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 算力中心普遍存在 GPU 利用率低下问题，源于 IO 墙、内存墙和重力墙的限制。",
      "explanation": "昂贵的 GPU 常因数据传输速度慢、模型参数超出显存容量、数据跨地域流动成本高而空转，导致资源浪费和效率瓶颈。"
    },
    {
      "point": "XSKY 通过 AIMesh 的“三网合一”架构创新，从根源解决 AI 数据流动的效率问题。",
      "explanation": "MeshFS 提升训练数据 I/O 性能，MeshSpace 实现 EB 级全局数据管理，MeshFusion 用低成本方案突破推理内存限制，应对 AI 基础设施深层挑战。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AIMesh 定位为中立、开放的数据底座，确保企业数据资产“常青”不受算力迭代影响。",
      "explanation": "通过解耦算力与数据，AIMesh 提供一致标准的数据服务接口，支持多元技术生态，为企业长期 AI 发展提供稳定基石。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "你花大价钱买的顶级 GPU，可能 30%时间都在「发呆」------不是算力不够，而是数据喂不上。",
    "AI 进化的道路上，横亘着三堵无形的高墙：IO 墙、内存墙和重力墙。",
    "XSKY 认为破局的关键在于架构创新。",
    "AIMesh 被定义为面向「AI 工厂」的数据与内存网，核心思路是用一套「三网合一」的柔性网络，替代传统僵化的存储架构。",
    "XSKY 星辰天合明确的战略选择是：开放解耦，做中立的数据底座。"
  ],
